- Fuck.
- Lad, come on. Sit down.

1219
01:38:41,708 --> 01:38:44,290
It was on the internet, right?

1220
01:38:47,208 --> 01:38:49,369
- Fergus, man!
- What are you doing?

1221
01:38:50,750 --> 01:38:52,035
Fergus? Fergus!

1222
01:38:55,083 --> 01:38:58,075
Fergus, for fuck's sake!
Where you going?

1223
01:38:58,208 --> 01:38:59,948
Fergus!

1224
01:39:00,083 --> 01:39:03,405
Fergus, man. Fuck's sake,
get out the fuckin' car.

1225
01:39:03,542 --> 01:39:05,328
- Fuck off.
- Fuckin' hell, Fergus!

1226
01:39:05,458 --> 01:39:07,494
Don't do anything stupid, Fergus.

1227
01:39:07,625 --> 01:39:11,789
Fergus, get out the car!
Fergus! Fuck's sake!

1228
01:39:12,833 --> 01:39:14,414
Fucking hell.

1229
01:39:41,917 --> 01:39:44,408
Inhale, and then exhale.

1230
01:39:46,083 --> 01:39:48,699
Lovely. Touch the ceiling.

1231
01:39:56,417 --> 01:39:58,954
And pull it back.

1232
01:39:59,083 --> 01:40:02,325
If you imagine that
you're against a wall,

1233
01:40:02,458 --> 01:40:05,950
and if you're against the wall,
keeping flat...

1234
01:40:43,375 --> 01:40:45,787
Raise your glasses...

1235
01:40:49,375 --> 01:40:51,206
..and the future.

1236
01:41:09,250 --> 01:41:11,017
I'll look forward to it.

1237
01:41:11,106 --> 01:41:12,913
Thank you very much. That was great today.

1238
01:41:13,042 --> 01:41:15,408
Thank you. Bye-bye, have a safe journey.

1239
01:41:20,208 --> 01:41:22,870
All right, gents.
Good to meet you both, at last.

1240
01:41:24,625 --> 01:41:26,581
See you when I get back.

1241
01:41:27,292 --> 01:41:28,998
Look forward to it.

1242
01:41:32,125 --> 01:41:34,741
Hayley, would you like a lift?
We're going your way.

1243
01:41:34,875 --> 01:41:36,661
That's very nice. Andrew?

1244
01:41:37,833 --> 01:41:40,449
I'd better not,
I've got lots of work to do. Thanks.

1245
01:41:50,292 --> 01:41:52,203
Andrew...

1246
01:41:56,125 --> 01:41:57,865
Open it.

1247
01:42:02,292 --> 01:42:05,250
- What is it, Alex?
- I'm not sure.

1248
01:42:12,042 --> 01:42:14,533
"Wrong place, wrong time."

1249
01:42:56,375 --> 01:42:58,286
It's me, Fergus.

1250
01:42:59,708 --> 01:43:01,323
Listen, I...

1251
01:43:02,375 --> 01:43:04,411
I saw you at the studio.

1252
01:43:05,542 --> 01:43:08,534
I really... wish...

1253
01:43:08,667 --> 01:43:10,953
I wanted to speak to you one more time,

1254
01:43:11,083 --> 01:43:13,665
But I just... I couldn't.

1255
01:43:13,792 --> 01:43:17,990
Just couldn't... bear it.
Couldn't face it.

1256
01:43:19,917 --> 01:43:21,657
Look, it's, er...

1257
01:43:24,417 --> 01:43:27,705
It's hard for a civvy
to understand this, but I just...

1258
01:43:29,167 --> 01:43:32,079
just wanted a piece of me old self back.

1259
01:43:33,625 --> 01:43:36,162
The way I was.

1260
01:43:36,292 --> 01:43:38,248
Wish you'd known me then.

1261
01:43:39,042 --> 01:43:42,534
There's things I need you to do.

1262
01:43:42,667 --> 01:43:45,374
I've spoken to a solicitor.

1263
01:43:45,500 --> 01:43:48,663
He knows what I want,
but I need your help.

1264
01:43:48,792 --> 01:43:50,953
You've got to go and see Harim.

1265
01:43:52,083 --> 01:43:55,655
Make sure that the Iraqi mother
and her family are taken care of.

1266
01:43:56,625 --> 01:43:58,707
Frankie wanted that.

1267
01:44:01,375 --> 01:44:05,914
Criminal sons of bitches on the make,
that's what we've been.

1268
01:44:09,208 --> 01:44:13,406
Look, I never told you this...

1269
01:44:14,417 --> 01:44:15,907
but, er...

1270
01:44:17,500 --> 01:44:19,240
I once saw this...

1271
01:44:20,583 --> 01:44:23,746
...this child pulled from the rubble
by her grandfather.

1272
01:44:25,875 --> 01:44:27,740
She wore a lilac top.

1273
01:44:30,417 --> 01:44:33,124
Her left leg dangled from a sinew.

1274
01:44:34,375 --> 01:44:36,240
Her feet, shredded.

1275
01:44:42,250 --> 01:44:44,787
She points at me when I try to sleep.

1276
01:44:50,250 --> 01:44:51,990
Heading off, now.

1277
01:44:53,333 --> 01:44:55,198
With Frankie.

1278
01:44:56,583 --> 01:44:58,539
Down by the river.

1279
01:45:00,792 --> 01:45:04,740
Best put a mad dog down
before it savages someone else.

1280
01:45:08,625 --> 01:45:10,536
Look after Craig for me.

1281
01:45:12,333 --> 01:45:14,244
I think he'll make it.

1282
01:45:15,625 --> 01:45:17,741
He just might need help with it.

1283
01:45:25,792 --> 01:45:27,874
Love you, Rachel.

1284
01:45:29,417 --> 01:45:31,499
I love you, Rachel.

1285
01:46:32,000 --> 01:46:41,300
